# These commands are here to streamline the installation process. If there is trouble installing the packages needed, 
please reference the commands below.

when we use conda to install pandas plink, make sure that the python environment you are using is the python environment from anaconda, 
otherwise, even if you install pandas plink using the command we gave them, it will not be in the correct python environment 

if you get this error message
"ImportError: DLL load failed while importing _imaging: The specified module could not be found."

reinstall pillow with:
pip uninstall pillow
pip install pillow
